{"word":"G4295 - πρόκειμαι - prókeimai - prok'-i-mahee - Be first","slug":"G4295","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρόκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>prókeimai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>prok'-i-mahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be first"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - prokeimai</b> - <i>prok'-i-mahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4253\">G4253</a> and <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>lie before</i> the view, that is, (figuratively) to <i>be present</i> (to the mind), to <i>stand forth</i> (as an example or reward): - be first, set before (forth)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2621\">G2621</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4029\">G4029</a>, <a href=\"#/G480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606\">G606</a>"}]}